---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Ch. Vormund Glastonbury — Shiba Inu Nº 1 do Brasil | Ninpozan Kennel"
  description="Ch. Vormund Glastonbury 'Banger': Shiba Inu Nº 1 do Brasil 2026, recordista de CACs e vitórias de grupo. Filho do Melhor Shiba do Mundo."
  ogImage="/banger-destaque.png"
  breadcrumbs={[{ name: "Nossos Cães", url: "/nossos-caes/" }, { name: "Ch. Vormund Glastonbury", url: "/nossos-caes/glastonbury/" }]}
>

  <section class="dog-page">
    <div class="container">

      <a href="/nossos-caes" class="back-link">← Nossos Cães</a>

      <header class="dog-header">
        <h1>Ch. Vormund Glastonbury</h1>
        <p class="dog-callname">"Banger"</p>
      </header>

      <div class="hero-photo panel">
        <img src="/banger-destaque.png" alt="Ch. Vormund Glastonbury - Banger" />
      </div>

      <div class="dog-info">
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="info-label">Nascimento</span>
          <span class="info-value">05/10/2024</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="info-label">Pais</span>
          <span class="info-value">Ch. Vormund Xmas Bonus & Ch. Vormund Lady Godiva</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="info-label">Genética & Exames</span>
          <span class="info-value genetic">AYAT EE | GM1 HEREDITARY CLEAR</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="conquistas-destaque panel">
        <div class="laurel-wrap">
          <svg class="laurel laurel-left" viewBox="0 0 60 120" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M30 115 C25 100, 8 95, 5 80 C2 65, 10 55, 12 45 C14 35, 8 25, 10 15 C12 8, 18 5, 25 3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            <ellipse cx="8" cy="78" rx="6" ry="10" transform="rotate(-20 8 78)" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
            <ellipse cx="10" cy="60" rx="5" ry="9" transform="rotate(-10 10 60)" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
            <ellipse cx="12" cy="43" rx="5" ry="8" transform="rotate(-5 12 43)" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
            <ellipse cx="11" cy="27" rx="4" ry="7" transform="rotate(5 11 27)" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
            <ellipse cx="15" cy="13" rx="4" ry="6" transform="rotate(15 15 13)" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
          </svg>
          <div class="conquistas-text">
            <p>Shiba Adulto e Jovem Nº 1 do Brasil 2026</p>
            <p>&</p>
            <p>Shiba Jovem Nº 1 — 2025</p>
          </div>
          <svg class="laurel laurel-right" viewBox="0 0 60 120" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M30 115 C35 100, 52 95, 55 80 C58 65, 50 55, 48 45 C46 35, 52 25, 50 15 C48 8, 42 5, 35 3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none"/>
            <ellipse cx="52" cy="78" rx="6" ry="10" transform="rotate(20 52 78)" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
            <ellipse cx="50" cy="60" rx="5" ry="9" transform="rotate(10 50 60)" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
            <ellipse cx="48" cy="43" rx="5" ry="8" transform="rotate(5 48 43)" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
            <ellipse cx="49" cy="27" rx="4" ry="7" transform="rotate(-5 49 27)" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
            <ellipse cx="45" cy="13" rx="4" ry="6" transform="rotate(-15 45 13)" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="dog-description">
        <p><strong>"Banger"</strong> tem uma linha de sangue incrível, ele é filho do cão que venceu a raça no Campeonato Mundial 2026, em Bolonha, tornando ele o filho do Melhor Shiba do Mundo.</p>
        <p><strong>"Banger"</strong> no Brasil é o atual recordista de CACs na raça, recordes em vencimento de grupos na raça.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="photo-grid">
        <div class="photo-square panel">
          <img src="/banger-sicalam.png" alt="Banger - SICALAM 2026" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="photo-square panel">
          <img src="/banger-cbkc.png" alt="Banger - Aniversário CBKC 2026" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="show-results panel">
        <h2>Resultados de Shows</h2>
        <ul class="results-list">
          <li>
            <span class="result-event">KCSP 2026 de Inverno</span>
            <span class="result-detail">5x Best of Breed & Group Placements</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="result-event">Campeonato Carioca 2026</span>
            <span class="result-detail">6x Best of Breed & 3x Group Placements</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="result-event">SICALAM 2026 — Punta Del Este</span>
            <span class="result-detail">6x Best of Breed</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="result-event">Aniversário CBKC 2026 — Brasília</span>
            <span class="result-detail">#5 Best Junior in Show — Judge: Jennifer Hubbard</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="result-event">KCSP 2025 de Verão</span>
            <span class="result-detail">2x Best of Breed & Group Placements</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="result-event">Aniversário CBKC 2025 — São Bento do Sul</span>
            <span class="result-detail">2x Best of Breed</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .back-link {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--sumi);
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .back-link:hover { color: var(--verde-rolex); }

  .dog-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .dog-header h1 {
    font-family: "Shippori Mincho B1", serif;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    color: var(--verde-deep);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .dog-callname {
    font-family: "Shippori Mincho B1", serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--dourado);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .hero-photo {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .dog-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--nanquim);
    background: var(--papel-escuro);
  }
  .info-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .info-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: var(--sumi-light);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .info-value {
    font-family: "Shippori Mincho B1", serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--nanquim);
  }
  .info-value.genetic {
    font-family: "Zen Kaku Gothic New", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--verde-rolex);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .conquistas-destaque {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--verde-deep);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .laurel-wrap {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .laurel {
    width: 40px;
    height: 80px;
    color: var(--dourado);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .conquistas-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
  }
  .conquistas-text p {
    font-family: "Shippori Mincho B1", serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--dourado);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .dog-description {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  .dog-description p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--sumi);
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .dog-description p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .dog-description strong { color: var(--nanquim); }

  .photo-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .photo-square {
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .photo-square img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .photo-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .show-results {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--papel-escuro);
  }
  .show-results h2 {
    font-family: "Shippori Mincho B1", serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--verde-deep);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .results-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.2rem;
  }
  .results-list li {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }
  .results-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }
  .result-event {
    font-family: "Shippori Mincho B1", serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--nanquim);
  }
  .result-detail {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--dourado-escuro);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .dog-header h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    .dog-callname { font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .laurel { width: 30px; height: 60px; }
    .conquistas-text p { font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .dog-info { padding: 1rem 1.2rem; }
  }
</style>
